        <abstract>
            <para>This is the majority of records collated, digitised and held by BIS excluding any records known or thought to be already on NBN Atlas for example county datasets, National Scheme and Society datasets, third party data and where the data provider has refused permission to share to the NBN Atlas.
Contact BIS for further information or go to website www.bis.org.uk for County recorder contacts.</para>
